item.title: The End of an Era!
item.description: The Day Has Come. I’m officially archiving my previous development plan and moving on to new adventures in Vipps Mobile Pay! It’s been a long time coming, and I’m happy to say that I’ve achieved most of the goals I set out to achieve. I’ve learned a lot, and I’m ready to proceed towards the next chapter. I’m not, however, ready to make a new plan just yet. So consider this post ceremonial more than anything.
